  "body": "Hello!\r\n\r\nI'd propose modifying the `index.html` in the `gh-pages` branch to contain the compiled Yellowpaper.\r\n\r\nIf you would like I can draft PR.\r\n\r\n**Todo**\r\n\r\n- [x] Let me know if you would like me to draft a PR\r\n\r\n**Background**\r\n\r\nI can imagine fellow devs finding it hard to read the yellowpaper on:\r\n\r\n- Phones\r\n- Smaller tablets\r\n- eReaders\r\n\r\nPersonally, I like importing content to my eReader (through Pocket integration) which handles PDF poorly. ",
